components.name: ButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<button
  [ngClass]="{
    button: true,
    'button-primary': css === 'button-primary' && !disabled,
    'button-secondary': css === 'button-secondary',
    'button-tertiary': css === 'button-tertiary',
    'bg-slate-400 text-white w-full transition-all h-9': disabled
  }"
  [type]="type"
  [class]="css"
  [disabled]="disabled"
>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</button>

components.name: ErrorInputComponent

propertiesClass.name: errorMessages
propertiesClass.defaultValue:
{
    required: () => ErrorMessages.EMPTY,
    email: () => ErrorMessages.INVALID_EMAIL,
    pattern: () => ErrorMessages.PATTERN,
    minlength: (booleanValue: BooleanValue = { requiredLength: 6 }) =>
      ErrorMessages.MIN_LENGTH(booleanValue),
    maxlength: (booleanValue: BooleanValue = { requiredLength: 50 }) =>
      ErrorMessages.MAX_LENGTH(booleanValue),
  }

components.templateData: {{ listOfErrors() }}
